-- BP Will Proceed With Gulf Well Pressure Test After Getting U.S. Clearance
-- Katarzyna Klimasinska
-- 2010-07-14T21:12:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-14/bp-will-proceed-with-gulf-well-pressure-test-after-getting-u-s-clearance.html

          
          
             BP Plc will proceed with pressure
testing on its leaking Gulf of Mexico well after getting U.S.
government approval, National Incident Commander Thad Allen
said.  
 The company will start testing later this evening and work
in six-hour intervals, Allen said on a conference call from New
Orleans.  
          
          


  


        